When he was 1 (1998), his mother was promoted to Second Class Master Sergeant (equivalent to Master Sergeant in the American Marine) in Taiwanese Marines, also in the same year Chun-Hsien was beginning to discover what he could do with his little body, and crawled across the floor.  When he was 2 years old (1999), he made friends with a boy named: Hai Yu, when he was approaching new millennium (2000), then his mother says that this new millennium will be the new one, when he was 3 years old (2000), his mother takes him to the doctor for vaccination, he tried to stay calm. That same year, Chun-Hsien went with his mother and his mutt Peluche to buy a new dog crate, and he gave Peluche some green beans (which the Peluche didn't like), and together with Hai they had their first sleepover in Ikea (hope their mothers don't ground them 😖). 

When he was 4 years old (2001), Chun-Hsien admitted that he broke their toilet after playing (his parents understood him). When he was 5 years old (2002), on the occasion of a family holiday party at Hai's house, he invited Chun-Hsien to play together  in PlayStation 2 games, he accepted (he preferred Xbox, but Hai liked it),

