== Senior High School & Draft to Major League Baseball ==

When he was 15 years old (2012), he graduated from Junior High School, then he started Senior High School, in the private school Jen Senior High School, others suggested him Football, because he is more popular, but he prefers Baseball, and he joined Senior High School Baseball Team. 
That same year, he fell in love with a girl named Ya-wen Teng, who met at the gym.  When he was 16 years old (2013), Ya-wen Teng wanted love to the next level, but when he learned that sexual activities at such a young age could be dangerous, Chun-Hsien refused, saying that he was not ready for these activities, so  she understood him and respected what he said.

When he was 17 years old (2014), Hai asked if Chun-Hsien would be his best friend and he said to keep the friendship the same way. When he was 18 years old (2015) he graduated from Senior High School, Chun-Hsien ran for a position in  2015 Major League Baseball draft, arrived at the draft site in the United States, with the subsequent intention of fulfilling the American dream (living in this country).  He was drafted as a second-round pick by the Texas Rangers, and after signing the contract, he moved with his girlfriend to play in Major League Baseball (MLB ⚾).  Once he did this, he took the driving test, his parents gave him money in New Taiwan Dollars to exchange for US Dollars and buy a car, and he chose a Mazda CX-3 for himself and his girlfriend.


